snippet.title: Jellyfish!  Learn about Jellyfish by Kids Learning Videos
snippet.description:
Jellyfish!
Learning about Jellyfish with this video.  This is a good video for children and kids who want to learn about Jellyfish.  Jellyfish are a very unique creature.  They live in the ocean and are many different colors and shapes.  This is a great video to learn about Jelly fish for children.
Thanks for watching Jellyfish!

snippet.title: Symmetrical Butterfly Painting | Caitie's Classroom | Learning Videos For Kids
snippet.description:
Want to learn how to paint symmetrical butterfly colors? Sit back and take notes as Caitie guides you step by step on how to make this butterfly craft! 

Caitie's Classroom airs LIVE every Tuesday at 11am ET here on the Super Simple play channel. Subscribe to Super Simple Paly and ring the bell to get notified when the livestream begins! ► https://bit.ly/2UIVNWy
